#: plugins/ocr/gocr/kookaocr-gocr.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<emphasis>GOCR</emphasis> (sometimes known as <emphasis>JOCR</emphasis>) is "
"an open source OCR engine, originally started by Joerg&nbsp;Schulenburg and "
"now with a team of active developers.<nl/><nl/>See <link url=\"http://jocr."
"sourceforge.net\">jocr.sourceforge.net</link> for more information on GOCR."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>GOCR</emphasis> (včasih znan tudi kot <emphasis>JOCR</emphasis>) "
"je odprtokodni mehanizem OCR, ki ga je prvotno začel Joerg&nbsp;Schulenburg, "
"zdaj pa z ekipo aktivnih razvijalcev.<nl/><nl/>Glejte <link url=\"http://"
"jocr.sourceforge.net\">jocr.sourceforge.net</link> za več informacij o GOCR."

#: plugins/ocr/ocrad/kookaocr-ocrad.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<emphasis>OCRAD</emphasis> is a free software OCR engine by Antonio&nbsp;"
"Diaz, part of the GNU&nbsp;Project.<nl/><nl/>Images for OCR should be "
"scanned in black/white (lineart) mode. Best results are achieved if the "
"characters are at least 20&nbsp;pixels high. Problems may arise, as usual, "
"with very bold or very light or broken characters, or with merged character "
"groups.<nl/><nl/>See <link url=\"http://www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html"
"\">www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html</link> for more information on "
"OCRAD."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>OCRAD</emphasis> je prosta programska oprema za OCR avtorja "
"Antonio&nbsp;Diaz, del projekta GNU.<nl/><nl/>Slike za OCR je treba optično "
"prebrati v črno-belem (lineart) načinu. Najboljši rezultati so doseženi, če "
"so znaki visoki vsaj 20&nbsp;pikslov. Težave se lahko običajno pojavijo z "
"zelo krepkimi ali zelo svetlimi ali zlomljenimi znaki ali z združenimi "
"skupinami znakov.<nl/><nl/>Glejte <link url=\"http://www.gnu.org/software/"
"ocrad /ocrad.html\">www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html</link> za več "
"informacij o OCRAD."

#: plugins/ocr/tesseract/kookaocr-tesseract.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Tesseract</emphasis> is a free software OCR engine, originally "
"developed at HP&nbsp;Labs and now sponsored by Google. It supports multiple "
"languages and scripts (including right-to-left text) and page layout "
"analysis.<nl/><nl/>The best results are achieved if scanned characters are "
"at least 20&nbsp;pixels high. Problems may arise with excessively skewed or "
"rotated images, or if dark borders are present.<nl/><nl/>See <link url="
"\"https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract\">github.com/tesseract-ocr/"
"tesseract</link> for more information on Tesseract."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Tesseract</emphasis> je mehanizem OCR proste programske opreme, "
"prvotno razvit v HP&nbsp;Labs, zdaj pa ga sponzorira Google. Podpira več "
"jezikov in pisav (vključno z besedilom od desne proti levi) ter analizo "
"postavitve strani.<nl/><nl/>Najboljše rezultate dosežete, če so skenirani "
"znaki visoki vsaj 20&nbsp;pikslov. Težave se lahko pojavijo pri preveč "
"poševnih ali zasukanih slikah ali če so prisotne temne obrobe.<nl/><nl/"
">Glejte <link url=\"https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract\">github.com/ "
"tesseract-ocr/tesseract</link> za več informacij o Tesseractu."
